<mxCell id="n65" value="&lt;b&gt;Other protocol surfaces (not on this happy path):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;OAuth 2.0&lt;/b&gt; Identity Linking — Agent ↔ Merchant /oauth/* (RFC 8414 + PKCE), scope order:read · REST&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;b&gt;3-DS escalation&lt;/b&gt; — PSP returns continue_url; User completes the step-up in the browser · REST&lt;br/&gt;• Approval inbox — autonomy-blocked buys wait for the User&#x27;s decision in Walletly · REST" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8fafc;strokeColor=#cbd5e1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;fontSize=10;fontColor=#334155;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="1410" width="470" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
